				<p class="postmetadata">06.02.2014 (Norbert Rost) Kategorie: <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/category/analysen/" title="Alle Beiträge in Analysen ansehen" rel="category tag">Analysen</a>, <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/category/die-kleinen-schritte/" title="Alle Beiträge in Die kleinen Schritte ansehen" rel="category tag">Die kleinen Schritte</a>, <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/category/presseschau/" title="Alle Beiträge in Presseschau ansehen" rel="category tag">Presseschau</a>  &middot; Tags: <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/tag/erfurt/" rel="tag">Erfurt</a>, <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/tag/grune/" rel="tag">Grüne</a>, <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/tag/peak-oil/" rel="tag">peak oil</a>, <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/tag/studie/" rel="tag">studie</a>, <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/tag/thuringen/" rel="tag">Thüringen</a>  &middot; <a href="http://www.peak-oil.com/2014/02/peak-oil-thueringen/#comments" title="Kommentiere Studie: Peak Oil &#8211; Herausforderung f&#252;r Th&#252;ringen">55 Kommentare &#187;</a> </p>

